author: Enterprise staff
title: Church cancels drive-through Nativity | News | davisenterprise.com
text:
Christ Church of Davis, 1801 Oak Ave., announced today it was canceling its drive-through Nativity display, scheduled for Thursday and Friday, due to bad weather.
